Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.graphhopper

Class GraphHopperEdgeProperties

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.graphhopper.GraphHopperEdgeProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
EdgeProperties
public class GraphHopperEdgeProperties extends Object implements EdgeProperties
Provides properties from the current EdgeIteratorState or its belonging Connection to be used by an RoutingCostFunction.
